der), Sarcelles</span> <!----> <!----></div> <!----></div> <div class="metainfo__actions metainfo__actions--longformvisual "><!----> <!----> <!----></div></div> <!----></a> <!----></div></div> <!----></article><article data-source-element-widget="" class="teaser--article teaser--slide teaser--slide-mobile-fullscreen "><div id="id-ld_1763548" data-nzz-tid="teaser" data-nzz-cid="doc-1hbb7qqci0" data-nzz-cp="2" data-nzz-ct="Unsere Empfehlungen" data-nzz-pic="8" class="teaser teaser__layout--longformstandard teaser--size-slide teaser--slide-mobile-fullscreen"><!----> <!----> <!----> <!----> <div class="poster poster--slide poster--slide-longformstandard"><figure class="poster__figure poster__figure--image"><a href="/feuilleton/kuenstlerpaar-heinz-helle-und-julia-weber-ld.1763548" data-nzz-referrer="teaserLink" class="teaser__link teaser__link--poster teaser__link--poster-slide"><div class="image-placeholder poster__placeholder"><img alt="«Haben wir eigentlich gesagt, wie privilegiert wir sind? Wie dankbar, immer wieder, für das alles?» Julia Weber und Heinz Helle vor dem Ferienhaus ihrer Eltern in Mon in Graubünden." src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" loading="lazy" srcset="https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/01/2ac7e2ca-9cc4-4ec2-a4f0-a67b5cce5d44.jpeg?width=320&amp;height=427&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=3081,4108,x526,y1613 320w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/01/2ac7e2ca-9cc4-4ec2-a4f0-a67b5cce5d44.jpeg?width=640&amp;height=853&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=3081,4108,x526,y1613 640w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/01/2ac7e2ca-9cc4-4ec2-a4f0-a67b5cce5d44.jpeg?width=270&amp;height=360&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=3081,4108,x526,y1613 270w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/01/2ac7e2ca-9cc4-4ec2-a4f0-a67b5cce5d44.jpeg?width=540&amp;height=720&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=3081,4108,x526,y1613 540w" width="3082" height="4108" class="image-placeholder__imag