na Oberholzer</span> <time datetime="2023-11-21T04:30:00.000Z" class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--date">21.11.2023</time> <span data-tooltip="Lesezeit 3 min" class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--reading-time"><svg version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="reading-time__icon nzz-icons--small nzz-icons--icon nzz-icons--fill"><path stroke="currentColor" fill="none" pid="0" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-linecap="round" _stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.77 7.39v5.62l3.8 1.32"/><circle stroke="currentColor" fill="none" pid="1" cx="12" cy="12" r="8.5" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-linecap="round" _stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> <span>3 min</span></span></div> <!----></div> <div class="metainfo__actions metainfo__actions--regular "><!----> <!----> <!----></div></div></div></div></article> <!----></div></div><div class="widget__row widget__row--no-child-last"><div data-nzz-tid="widget-1of3" data-source-element-widget="Widget-1/3-Breite" id="id-doc-1hfosd1p115" content="" pagetype="Page" componenttype="widget--1of3-article" class="widget--1of3 widget--article widget--no-child-last"><!----> <article data-nzz-tid="" article-embed="" data-source-element-widget="" class="teaser--article teaser--1of3"><div id="id-ld_1766597" data-nzz-tid="teaser" data-nzz-cid="doc-1h5h9dcpt0" data-nzz-cp="3" data-nzz-ct="" data-nzz-pic="3" data-teaser-mobile-option="teaser-mobile-standard" class="teaser teaser__layout--regular teaser--size-1of3"><!----> <!----> <!----> <!----> <div class="poster poster--1of3 poster--1of3-regular"><figure class="poster__figure poster__figure--image"><a href="/international/ist-argentinien-bereit-fuer-ihn-der-anarcho-libertaere-javier-milei-wird-naechster-praesident-argentiniens-ld.1766597" data-nzz-referrer="teaserLink" class="teaser__link teaser__link--poster teaser__link--poster-1of3"><div class="image-placeholder poster__placeholder" style="padding-bottom:56.25%;"><img alt="Javier Mileis unheimlicher Blick ist zum Markenzeichen des neuen Präsidenten gewo