    Kommentar
  </span> <!----> <!----></div> <h2 class="teaser__title teaser__title--slide teaser__title--opinion teaser__title--7"><!----> <!----> <span class="teaser__title-name teaser__title-name--waiting">Berset und die Mail-Affäre: An Monsieur Teflon bleibt nichts kleben</span></h2> <!----> <!----> <!----></div> <!----> <!----> <!----></a> <div bookmark-type="article" bookmark-sub-type="teaser" class="metainfo metainfo--slide metainfo--opinion"><div class="metainfo__main metainfo__main--opinion"><!----> <div class="metainfo__wrapper"><span class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--author">Christina Neuhaus</span> <time datetime="2023-11-17T19:16:46.623Z" class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--date">17.11.2023</time> <span data-tooltip="Lesezeit 3 min" class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--reading-time"><svg version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="reading-time__icon nzz-icons--small nzz-icons--icon nzz-icons--fill"><path stroke="currentColor" fill="none" pid="0" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-linecap="round" _stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.77 7.39v5.62l3.8 1.32"/><circle stroke="currentColor" fill="none" pid="1" cx="12" cy="12" r="8.5" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-linecap="round" _stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> <span>3 min</span></span></div> <!----></div> <div class="metainfo__actions metainfo__actions--opinion "><!----> <!----> <!----></div></div></div></div> <!----></article> <!----></flickity></div></div></div></section></div><div id="contdoc-1h5h9f1ng0-1747637" never="" class="elementwrap"><section data-source-element="Container-Mobile-First" data-nzz-tid="container-exclusive" data-nzz-container="" data-nzz-vob="pageelement--mobilefirst--v4" id="" content="" class="pageelement pageelement--container--mobilefirst pageelement--mobilefirst--v4 no-color-scheme"><div class="pageelement__inner"><!----> <div><div class="widget__row widget__row--no-child-last"><div data-nzz-tid="widget-3of3" data-source-element-widget="Widget-Volle-Breite" id="id-doc-1hfosd1p21" content="" p