ischen: Eva Bruhns (Katharina Stark) in Episode 4. (Krzysztof Wiktor)" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" loading="lazy" srcset="https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/17/26a6e5f3-090e-46d4-9793-195f13eec181.jpeg?width=520&amp;height=292&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=5168,2903,x0,y0 520w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/17/26a6e5f3-090e-46d4-9793-195f13eec181.jpeg?width=1040&amp;height=584&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=5168,2903,x0,y0 1040w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/17/26a6e5f3-090e-46d4-9793-195f13eec181.jpeg?width=464&amp;height=261&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=5168,2907,x0,y0 464w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/17/26a6e5f3-090e-46d4-9793-195f13eec181.jpeg?width=928&amp;height=522&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=5168,2907,x0,y0 928w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/17/26a6e5f3-090e-46d4-9793-195f13eec181.jpeg?width=352&amp;height=198&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=5168,2907,x0,y0 352w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/17/26a6e5f3-090e-46d4-9793-195f13eec181.jpeg?width=704&amp;height=396&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=5168,2907,x0,y0 704w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/17/26a6e5f3-090e-46d4-9793-195f13eec181.jpeg?width=380&amp;height=214&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=5168,2907,x0,y0 380w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/17/26a6e5f3-090e-46d4-9793-195f13eec181.jpeg?width=760&amp;height=427&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=5168,2907,x0,y0 760w" width="5168" height="2907" class="image-placeholder__image poster__image"> <!----> <!----> <!----></div></a></figure></div> <!----> <div class="teaser__content teaser__content--1of2"><a href="/feuilleton/deutsches-haus-ld.1765522" data-nzz-referrer="teaserLink" ordinal-number="2" class="teaser__link"><div class="teaser__wrapper"><!----> <!----> <h2 class="teaser__title teaser__title--1of2 teaser__title--longformstandard teaser__title--1"><!---