g muss sich neu erfinden</span></h2> <!----> <!----> <!----></div> <!----> <!----> <!----></a> <div bookmark-type="article" bookmark-sub-type="teaser" class="metainfo metainfo--slide metainfo--longformstandard"><div class="metainfo__main metainfo__main--longformstandard"><!----> <div class="metainfo__wrapper"><span class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--author">Peter A. Fischer</span> <time datetime="2023-11-17T10:00:00.000Z" class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--date">17.11.2023</time> <span data-tooltip="Lesezeit 7 min" class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--reading-time"><svg version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="reading-time__icon nzz-icons--small nzz-icons--icon nzz-icons--fill"><path stroke="currentColor" fill="none" pid="0" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-linecap="round" _stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.77 7.39v5.62l3.8 1.32"/><circle stroke="currentColor" fill="none" pid="1" cx="12" cy="12" r="8.5" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-linecap="round" _stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> <span>7 min</span></span></div> <!----></div> <div class="metainfo__actions metainfo__actions--longformstandard "><!----> <!----> <!----></div></div></div></div> <!----></article><article data-source-element-widget="" class="teaser--article teaser--slide "><div id="id-ld_1765473" data-nzz-tid="teaser" data-nzz-cid="doc-1h5h9ds5e0" data-nzz-cp="9" data-nzz-ct="PRO Global" data-nzz-pic="5" class="teaser teaser__layout--regular teaser--size-slide"><!----> <!----> <!----> <!----> <div class="poster poster--slide poster--slide-regular"><figure class="poster__figure poster__figure--image"><a href="/pro-global/proglobal-die-aussichten-fuer-argentiniens-wirtschaft-sind-gut-fuer-die-naechste-regierung-eher-nicht-ld.1765473" data-nzz-referrer="teaserLink" class="teaser__link teaser__link--poster teaser__link--poster-slide"><div class="image-placeholder poster__placeholder" style="padding-bottom:75%;"><img alt="Wer von den beiden gewinnen wird, ist völlig offen: der libertäre Ökonom Javier Milei (links) oder der Wirtschaftsminister Sergio Massa. Sie liegen Kopf an Kopf in den Umfragen. (Luis Robayo / AP)" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" loading="lazy" srcset="https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/13/23c88f54-0b91-43db-9b7a-24f0644c090b.jpeg?width=242&amp;height=182&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=4228,3179,x891,y467 242w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/13/23c88f54-0b91-43db-9b7a-24f0644c090b.jpeg?width=484&amp;height=364&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=4228,3179,x891,y467 484w" width="4239" height="3179" class="image-placeholder__image poster__image"> <!----> <!----> <!----></div></a></figure></div> <!----> <div class="teaser__content teaser__content--slide"><a href="/pro-global/proglobal-die-aussichten-fuer-argentiniens-wirtschaft-sind-gut-fuer-die-naechste-regierung-eher-nicht-ld.1765473" data-nzz-referrer="teaserLink" ordinal-number="5" class="teaser__link"><div class="teaser__wrapper"><!----> <div class="teaser__flag teaser__flag--colored teaser__flag--slide teaser__flag--slide-regular"><!----> <!----> <svg version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 32 16" class="icon--pro-nzz nzz-icons--icon nzz-icons--fill" style="width:32px;height:16px;"><rect pid="0" width="32" height="16" rx="4" fill="#000"/><path pid="1" d="M9.022 4.183H6v7.634h1.387V8.86h1.624c1.645 0 2.677-.914 2.677-2.355 0-1.408-1.043-2.322-2.666-2.322zm-.259 3.623H7.387V5.247h1.376c.904 0 1.463.495 1.463 1.28 0 .796-.56 1.28-1.463 1.28zM17.224 11.817h1.526L16.933 8.57c1.13-.323 1.602-1.183 1.602-2.097 0-1.258-.677-2.29-2.645-2.29h-3.075v7.634h1.387V8.753h1.344l1.678 3.064zm-3.022-6.58h1.452c1.043 0 1.43.505 1.43 1.236 0 .72-.387 1.247-1.43 1.247h-1.452V5.237zM22.978 12c2.194 0 3.613-1.538 3.613-4 0-2.484-1.42-4-3.613-4s-3.613 1.516-3.613 4c0 2.44 1.42 4 3.613 4zm0-1.118c-1.365 0-2.172-1.119-2.172-2.882 0-1.796.807-2.882 2.172-2.882 1.377 0 2.172 1.086 2.172 2.882s-.795 2.882-2.172 2.882z" fill="#fff"/></svg></div> <h2 class="tease