eere postkoloniale Astrologie» – wie die populärste Satireshow Israels die Hamas und ihre Anhänger verspottet</span></h2> <!----> <!----> <!----></div> <!----> <!----> <!----></a> <div bookmark-type="article" bookmark-sub-type="teaser" class="metainfo metainfo--mostread metainfo--longformstandard"><div class="metainfo__main metainfo__main--longformstandard"><!----> <div class="metainfo__wrapper"><span class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--author">Birgit Schmid</span> <time datetime="2023-11-20T04:30:00.000Z" class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--date">20.11.2023</time> <span data-tooltip="Lesezeit 6 min" class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--reading-time"><svg version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="reading-time__icon nzz-icons--small nzz-icons--icon nzz-icons--fill"><path stroke="currentColor" fill="none" pid="0" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-linecap="round" _stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.77 7.39v5.62l3.8 1.32"/><circle stroke="currentColor" fill="none" pid="1" cx="12" cy="12" r="8.5" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-linecap="round" _stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> <span>6 min</span></span></div> <!----></div> <div class="metainfo__actions metainfo__actions--longformstandard "><!----> <!----> <!----></div></div></div></div> <!----></article><article data-source-element-widget="" class="teaser--article teaser--mostread "><div id="id-ld_1766545" data-nzz-tid="teaser" data-nzz-cid="doc-1h5h9fqc20" data-nzz-cp="10" data-nzz-ct="" data-nzz-pic="3" class="teaser teaser__layout--opinion teaser--size-mostread"><!----> <!----> <!----> <!----> <!----> <!----> <div class="teaser__content teaser__content--mostread teaser__content--numbered"><a href="/meinung/warum-waehlt-argentinien-den-ultraliberalen-milei-zum-praesidenten-ld.1766545" data-nzz-referrer="teaserLink" ordinal-number="3" class="teaser__link"><div class="teaser__wrapper"><!----> <div class="teaser__flag teaser__flag--colored teaser__flag--mostread teaser__flag--mostread-opinion"><span class="teaser__flag--tex