hauser ihn als ersten SP-Mann überhaupt in den Ständerat gewählt haben. (Walter Bieri / Keystone)" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" loading="lazy" srcset="https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/20/c1c76420-f4a8-4db1-b0cb-0049436e043d.jpeg?width=319&amp;height=180&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=3329,1878,x2391,y562 319w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/20/c1c76420-f4a8-4db1-b0cb-0049436e043d.jpeg?width=638&amp;height=360&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=3329,1878,x2391,y562 638w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/20/c1c76420-f4a8-4db1-b0cb-0049436e043d.jpeg?width=292&amp;height=164&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=3338,1875,x2391,y562 292w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/20/c1c76420-f4a8-4db1-b0cb-0049436e043d.jpeg?width=584&amp;height=328&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=3338,1875,x2391,y562 584w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/20/c1c76420-f4a8-4db1-b0cb-0049436e043d.jpeg?width=223&amp;height=125&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=3338,1872,x2391,y562 223w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/20/c1c76420-f4a8-4db1-b0cb-0049436e043d.jpeg?width=446&amp;height=250&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=3338,1872,x2391,y562 446w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/20/c1c76420-f4a8-4db1-b0cb-0049436e043d.jpeg?width=380&amp;height=214&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=3338,1878,x2391,y562 380w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/20/c1c76420-f4a8-4db1-b0cb-0049436e043d.jpeg?width=760&amp;height=427&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=3338,1878,x2391,y562 760w" width="3338" height="1878" class="image-placeholder__image poster__image"> <!----> <!----> <!----></div></a></figure></div> <!----> <div class="teaser__content teaser__content--1of3-compact"><a href="/schweiz/simon-stocker-so-hat-der-sp-mann-den-abzockerschreck-minder-in-die-politikerrente-geschickt-ld.1766644" data-nzz-referrer="teaserLink" ordinal-number="1" class="teaser__lin