    Interview
  </span> <!----> <!----></div> <h2 class="teaser__title teaser__title--1of3 teaser__title--longformvisual teaser__title--0"><!----> <!----> <span class="teaser__title-name teaser__title-name--waiting">Herr Vuignier, wie tötet man einen Wolf?</span></h2> <!----> <div class="teaser__lead teaser__lead--1of3 teaser__lead--longformvisual">Ab 1.&#160;Dezember sind zwei Drittel der Schweizer Wölfe zum Abschuss freigegeben. Aber bekommt man sie überhaupt vor den Gewehrlauf? Ein Gespräch mit dem Jäger Pascal Vuignier über die Tücken und den Reiz der Wolfsjagd.</div> <!----></div> <!----> <!----> <!----></a> <div bookmark-type="article" bookmark-sub-type="teaser" class="metainfo metainfo--1of3 metainfo--longformvisual"><div class="metainfo__main metainfo__main--longformvisual"><!----> <div class="metainfo__wrapper"><span class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--author">Andrea Kučera und Alan Cassidy</span> <time datetime="2023-11-18T20:45:00.000Z" class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--date">18.11.2023</time> <!----></div> <!----></div> <div class="metainfo__actions metainfo__actions--longformvisual "><!----> <!----> <!----></div></div></div></div> <!----></article> <article data-source-element-widget="" class="teaser--article teaser--1of3 "><div id="id-ld_1765395" data-nzz-tid="teaser" data-nzz-cid="doc-1hf3mv7570" data-nzz-cp="14" data-nzz-ct="" data-nzz-pic="3" class="teaser teaser__layout--regular teaser--nzzas teaser--size-1of3"><!----> <!----> <!----> <!----> <div class="poster poster--1of3 poster--1of3-regular"><figure class="poster__figure poster__figure--image"><a href="https://magazin.nzz.ch/nzz-am-sonntag/kultur/die-summe-aller-frauen-folge-38-ld.1765395" no-prefetch="" data-nzz-referrer="teaserLink" class="teaser__link teaser__link--poster teaser__link--poster-1of3"><div class="image-placeholder poster__placeholder" style="padding-bottom:56.25%;"><img alt="Die Summe aller Frauen – Folge 38" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" loading="lazy" srcset="https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/13/f8759abb-5ce4-4b80-bb32-61b0f59d8167.jpeg?width=319&amp;height=180&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=7337,4140,x0,y386 319w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/13/f8759abb-5ce4-4b80-bb32-61b0f59d8167.jpeg?width=638&amp;height=360&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=7337,4140,x0,y386 638w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/13/f8759abb-5ce4-4b80-bb32-61b0f59d8167.jpeg?width=292&amp;height=164&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=7360,4134,x0,y386 292w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/13/f8759abb-5ce4-4b80-bb32-61b0f59d8167.jpeg?width=584&amp;height=328&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=7360,4134,x0,y386 584w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/13/f8759abb-5ce4-4b80-bb32-61b0f59d8167.jpeg?width=223&amp;height=125&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=7360,4126,x0,y386 223w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/13/f8759abb-5ce4-4b80-bb32-61b0f59d8167.jpeg?width=446&amp;height=250&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=7360,4126,x0,y386 446w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/13/f8759abb-5ce4-4b80-bb32-61b0f59d8167.jpeg?width=380&amp;height=214&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=7360,4140,x0,y386 380w, https://img.nzz.ch/2023/11/13/f8759abb-5ce4-4b80-bb32-61b0f59d8167.jpeg?width=760&amp;height=427&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=75&amp;auto=webp&amp;crop=7360,4140,x0,y386 760w" width="7360" height="4140" class="image-placeholder__image poster__image"> <!----> <!----> <!----></div></a></figure></div> <!----> <div class="teaser__content teaser__content--1of3"><a href="https://magazin.nzz.ch/nzz-am-sonntag/kultur/die-summe-aller-frauen-folge-38-ld.1765395" no-prefetch="" data-nzz-referrer="teaserLink" ordinal-number="1" class="teaser__link"><div class="teaser__wrapper"><!----> <!----> <h2 class="teaser__title teaser__title--1of3 teaser__title--regular teaser__title--0"><!----> <!----> <span class="teaser__title-name teaser__title-name--waiting">Die Summe aller Frauen – Folge 38</span></h2> <!----> <div class="teaser__lead teaser__lead--1of3 teaser__lead--regular">Die 38.&#160;Folge des Fortsetzungsromans von Jan Weiler. Bei Claudia wird’s ernst. Sie will ein Kind mit ihm. Und wird auch schwanger. Aber wie?</div> <!----></div> <!----> <!----> <!----></a> <div bookmark-type="article" bookmark-sub-type="teaser" class="metainfo metainfo--1of3 metainfo--regular"><div class="metainfo__main metainfo__main--regular"><!----> <div class="metainfo__wrapper"><span class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--author">Jan Weiler</span> <time datetime="2023-11-18T20:45:00.000Z" class="metainfo__item metainfo__item--date">18.11.2023</time> <!----></div> <!----></div> <div class="metainfo__actions metainfo__actions--regular "><!----> <!----> <!----></div></div></div></div> <!----></article></div></div></div></section></div><div class="widget__row widget__row--no-divider widget__row--no-child-last"><section data-source-element="Container-Store-Article-Magazin" data-nzz-tid="container-store-article-magazin" data-nzz-container="" id="id-doc-1hf3n0m8j0" content="" pagetype="Page" componenttype="widget--store-article-magazin" class="pageelement container-store--article-magazin"><div class="pageelement__inner elementwrap"><div class="widget__row"><div data-source-element-widget class="widget--articlelist"><article data-source-element-widget="" class="teaser--article teaser--articlelist "><div id="id-ld_1698961" data-nzz-tid="teaser" data-nzz-cid="doc-1hf3mv7570" data-nzz-cp="14" data-nzz-ct="" data-nzz-pic="4" class="teaser teaser__layout--alias-teaser teaser--size-articlelist"><!----> <a href="https://magazin.nzz.ch/nzz-am-sonntag" no-prefetch="" data-nzz-referrer="teaserLink" class="teaser__link teaser__link--mobile-title"><span class="teaser__title-name--mobile teaser__title-name--waiting">Lesen Sie die «NZZ am Sonntag» digital</span></a> <!----> <!----> <div class="poster poster--articlelist poster--articlelist-alias-teaser"><figure clas